The VOTER Protocol is intended as public-good substrate for verified civic
communication. The cryptographic primitives, contracts, and specs in this
repository are open for federation, peer implementation, and independent
audit. Communiqué PBC is the initial primary author and current maintainer
of the reference implementation; the licenses below do not grant Communiqué
PBC exclusive control over the protocol or its specifications. Peer
implementations are welcome under the terms of those licenses.

